          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Enter a game where the world is bright and colourful and you've just joined a literature club full of cute girls - nothing could go wrong, right? Well, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Doki Doki Literature Club Plus! ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "turns the anime visual novel genre upside down with psychological horror that will have you question everything that this supposedly innocent visual novel is telling you. Without spoiling too much, it's safe to assume that not everything is pink and rosey here in this innocent-looking after school club.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
